<form action="/" method="POST">
  This is an application where you write words on a piece of paper with four different colored pencils. You will see a report of your actions at the end.
  <br>
  <br>
  Would you like to create OrangePencil with .5 or .7 lead? (Choose .5 to be able to write up to 30 characters or .7 to be able to write up to 50 characters.)
  <br>
  <input type="radio" id=".5" name="lead" value=".5" required="required">
  <label for=".5"> .5 </label>
  <input type="radio" id=".7" name="lead" value=".7" required="required">
  <label for=".7"> .7 </label>
  <br>

  Write some words on the paper with OrangePencil:
  <br>
  <input type="text" name="answer">

  <input type="submit">

</form>
